SUMMARY:One Foot in Front of the Other
DESCRIPTION:62 min | English and Hindi with English Subtitles \nThe film follows four runners on their route from Bengaluru to Chennai along the highway. No formal organisation\, no personal bests to beat\, no reward at the finish line. They run for the joy of it\, for the community\, for the adventure. Filmmaker Basav Biradar saw this as a radical act\, under a hypercapitalist system\, to pursue a goal with no end except unto itself. He follows the runners with his camera to understand their motivations\, the physical and mental training\, and their friendship. \nThe screening will be followed by an audience Q&A with the runners and filmmaker\, moderated by Gautam Sonti. \n\n\nThe Road\, the Run\, the Why\nRSVP here (https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScajUl6bcJw-TogrwKPjUyn2zJCeyOr39DmqbSY4PSph_kjZw/viewform?usp=pp_url)\n*Speakers*: Basav Biradar\, Santhosh Padmanabhan\, Chandra Gopalan\, Krishan Dhall\, Manikandan Seran\, Gautam Sonti\n*Event Categories*: Film\, Media\, Sports
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/one-foot-in-front-of-the-other/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Film,Media,Sports
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/ThumbnailOFFO.jpg
END:VEVENT
