SUMMARY:Slytrix
DESCRIPTION:\nA blues guitarist and a Carnatic veena player walk onto the same stage. \nSlytrix is a neo-fusion duo featuring Sylvester Pradeep (Slyfly) and Santosh Jayaram (Ragatrix). Sylvester is a Bangalore-based guitarist and vocalist known for his work with Sylvester’s Trio and Sly Fly and the Blues Company\, with roots in the blues yet expansive and inventive in style. Santosh plays raga-based music on the electric Veena\, blending Carnatic tradition with Western harmony and blues influences.  \nTogether\, they build original music that moves past conventional fusion into something harder to place. \nSupported by:\n \n\n\n\nAn Odyssey of Rhythm\, Blues\, Raga and Resonance\nRSVP here (https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScMuYJtc-UgwYcuzwODI3NLEudsw_Y8oM04fm25rY_GUJecVg/viewform?usp=pp_url)\n*Performers*: Sylvester Pradeep\, Santosh Jayaram\n*Event Categories*: Music\, Performing Arts
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/slytrix/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Music,Performing Arts
